{"tid":1555197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有\"小熊維尼\"在德國國會前   聲援香港抗議","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:23:50.000Z","uid":41818,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be3ecf886d9ec7043eebd060830894d0cf5fa0f7","tid":1555197,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://stimme-de.de/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/photo_2019-09-09_10-30-45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstimme-de.de%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fphoto_2019-09-09_10-30-45.jpg&h=822d8c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://stimme-de.de/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/70017127_2433476086739200_5975634779708588032_n-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstimme-de.de%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F70017127_2433476086739200_5975634779708588032_n-2.jpg&h=96b818ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;高舉聲援香港標語出現在德國柏林的國會大廈前、猶太人大屠殺紀念碑林等柏林知名地標建築前。近年&ldquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;漸成網友諷刺中共當局最高領導人習近平的象徵形象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://stimme-de.de/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/IMG_7716-800x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstimme-de.de%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FIMG_7716-800x600.jpg&h=e49d89b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早在8月17日，在德國的香港留學生和其他人士於亞歷山大廣場舉辦的聲援香港抗議和平集會上，他們在簽名台前放置了一隻&ldquo;爆掉右眼&rdquo;的&ldquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9月8日，有網友扮成&rdquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;，其頭部和右眼位置&ldquo;染血&rdquo;，以指控港警對示威者濫施暴力和爆眼少女事件。 &ldquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;還手持大幅的&ldquo;自​​由香港&rdquo;（Free Hongkong）、反對中國納粹（Anti-Chinaizi）、立即民主（democracy now）的標語，在德國國會大廈以及猶太人大屠殺紀念碑林等柏林知名地標建築前拍下一系列有創意的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n早在2014年，習近平訪美時會見美國前總統奧巴馬，兩人並肩而行的照片被網友指與迪士尼電影中「小熊維尼」和它的朋友「跳跳虎」一起走路的形像神似；<br />\n<br />\n2014年11月，習近平與日本首相安倍晉三會談，網友再用維尼的電影卡通形像圖片對比。帶有嘲諷意味的圖片開始引發中國審查部門的關注。<br />\n<br />\n2015年習近平在紀念「二戰」結束70週年閱兵儀式上，乘坐一輛黑色的豪華轎車檢閱部隊。再有網友用小熊維尼站在一輛玩具卡車上的圖片模仿習近平的形象。<br />\n<br />\n自2017年&ldquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;漸成公眾反對習近平的象徵，「小熊維尼」、「維尼熊」等文字和相關的圖片，甚至表情包在中國大陸遭封殺。連帶《摯友難尼》的電影也遭禁映。<br />\n<br />\n香港抗議危機，中共當局被指隱身其後操控港府，一再升級的港警暴力、中共當局發動宣傳機器抹黑、集結軍隊威脅等遭全球輿論關切和批評。<br />\n<br />\n網友發起的此次&ldquo;小熊維尼&rdquo;創意活動已在網絡上迅速傳播，料將被迅速復制。香港抗議者及聲援者的抗議活動，完美擊敗中共單一刻板的宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stimme-de.de/2019/09/09/4896/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstimme-de.de%2F2019%2F09%2F09%2F4896%2F&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BulxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=c13bb4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://stimme-de.de/2019/09/09/4896/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SDeutschlands/status/1170979596294131714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSDeutschlands%2Fstatus%2F1170979596294131714&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BulxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=121fe736\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSDeutschlands%2Fstatus%2F1170979596294131714&h=3c5c09cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SDeutschlands/status/1170979596294131714</a>"},{"pid":"fe4ac9bafc519da26cc1628e13ef2dfb0be3ee5b","tid":1555197,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc24e53930a2c0dcd28ab5bc7f141551a02d8d8","tid":1555197,"uid":192848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"推行動post"},{"pid":"77fe60fb5f2240698f81b72412d5420295110f6e","tid":1555197,"uid":284304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:24:41.000Z","msg":"德國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff42c51b763fda8d7d380b7d58c3a68884d7f1d","tid":1555197,"uid":49066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:25:47.000Z","msg":"Respect"},{"pid":"e4dc66fb4bc952ec190ca2f6b53164dd3c8b8180","tid":1555197,"uid":291491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09